description: Try our easy to follow Raspberry & Coconut Marshmallow Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Raspberry & Coconut Marshmallow Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Secure the larger cake (see tip). Spread tops of both cakes with remaining jam and icing. Position smaller cake on top of larger cake, to one side. To serve, decorate with raspberries and shredded coconut.
